    "Body": " OKCoin is one of the world's first and largest regulated digital asset exchanges, with millions of users in more than 100 countries around the world. Founded in 2013, we provide traders and institutions with a fiat-to-token trading platform for digital assets including Bitcoin, Bitcoin Cash, Ethereum, Ethereum Classic, and Litecoin, with more assets coming soon. Offering fast trades and industry-leading expertise and support, our mission is to help eliminate trading barriers and improve transaction efficiency while complying with the highest regulatory standards in the US and the world. We are a passionate team of writers, designers, and product nerds dedicated to bringing the OKCoin experience to international markets. We are looking for a highly motivated content translation expert who is excited to ensure that the trading experiences we offer on our platform are equally enjoyable in other countries as it is in the US. As a content translator and localization expert, you take the convoluted world of cryptocurrency trading and blockchain and make it easy to understand. If you care as much about how screens flow into each other as you do what the words on them say, you'll fit right in. Skills (What You'll Have) At least 2 years of experience as a content translator Fluency in Spanish is required Broad understanding of the many skills that fit under the title of UX Writer, including problem definition, working directly with user flows, maintaining and evolving guidelines, and of course, writing. Positive, collaborative attitude with a passion for creating, editing, and translating online content. A solid portfolio of outstanding writing samples in your language of expertise. Attention to detail and a proven ability to manage priorities. Experience in a multi-language publishing environment, including globalization for translation and terminology databases and management. Experience thriving in a fast-paced development environment. Passion for crypto and blockchain innovations. Responsibilities (What Your Typical Day Looks Like) Plan, write, edit, translate and improve the current and new content including user interface language, microcopy, help content, labels, and navigation. Bring clarity to ambiguity as you conduct content audits Foster relationships and partner with key stakeholders to develop translation strategy and roadmap for your locale Work to evolve editorial and tone of voice content standards in your local language to deliver high-quality copy within tight timelines. Embrace a culture of feedback, sharing your work early and often. Navigate a fast-paced environment with team members in different time zones by balancing independent self-direction with frequent collaboration and open communication. Establish and ensure high-quality localization standards Advocate for the importance of copy and content strategy as a core element of creating great user experiences. OKCoin Statement OKCoin is committed to equal employment opportunities regardless of race, color, genetic information, creed, religion, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, lawful alien status, national origin, age, marital status, and non-job related physical or mental disability, or protected veteran status. Pursuant to the San Francisco Fair Chance Ordinance, we will consider for employment qualified applicants with arrest and conviction records.Show moreShow less ", 
